{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1689-03a_195","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"[Ouvrage de Mr le Pays]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mars 1689 (première partie) [tome 3], p. 195-202.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},{"#1":{"value":"Il me reste à vous parler d’un Ouvrage dont vous pourrez juger par vous mesme, puis que je vous en envoye une copie. Il a receu icy beaucoup de loüanges, &amp; je suis fort seur que vous le trouveriez d’un fort bon goust, quand je ne vous dirois pas que c’est M","id":"/div/p[1]/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p[1]/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" le Pays qui en est l’Auteur. Vous connoissez son stile enjoüé. Aprés beaucoup de poursuites pour l’obliger à payer une somme tres-considerable dont un Traitant pretendoit le rendre garant, il en a esté enfin déchargé par un Arrest du Conseil, &amp; c’est là-dessus qu’il a fait les Vers que vous allez lire.","id":"/div/p[1]/#2"}}],"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#1":{"value":"A M. Le CONTROLEUR","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"General.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aprés de si longues allarmes","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La paix est chez moy de retour,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je dors la nuit, je ris le jour,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du repos je sens tous les charmes.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfin me voila déchargé","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du procés où j’estois plongé.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand tout prest à faire naufrage","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le secours arrive à propos,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus on a tremblé dans l’orage,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et mieux on goûte le repos.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Seigneur, puis-je sans vous deplaire","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous faire un recit ingenu","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De l’estat où je me suis vû","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pendant le cours de mon affaire ?","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’un air inquiet j’observois","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tous les Huissiers que je trouvois :","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Certain Ecrit, signé Coquille,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"M’ayant declaré debiteur,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Fort-l’Evesque &amp; la Bastille","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A tous momens me faisoient peur.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mon destin estoit déplorable.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Me connoissant, qui le croira ?","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je languissois à l’Opera ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’estois rêveur &amp; triste à table.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans la peur d’une garnison","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’avois démeublé ma maison ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ma vaisselle craignant la guerre,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Estoit dans un Convent voisin :","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’estois reduit aux plats de terre","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ainsi qu’un pauvre Capucin.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Au grenier ma Tapisserie","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Estoit à la mercy des Rats :","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je n’avois chez moy que deux draps","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avec un lit de Friperie.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans ce lit, au lieu de dormir,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je passois la nuit à gemir,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ma frayeur n’avoit point de tréve","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le matin, dans mon Oraison,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je disois, mon Dieu, je me leve","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour coucher peut-estre en Prison.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Quelquefois au fort de mes peines,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Me croyant déja prisonnier,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avec de l’encre &amp; du papier","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’esperois adoucir mes chaînes.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’y pretendois tracer en vers","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De mon Roy les Exploits divers :","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais en prison peut-on écrire ?","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mon feu bien-tost s’y fût éteint ;","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est-là justement qu’on peut dire,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que le Poëte est fort contraint.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Je ne sçay point chanter en cage,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le grand air plaist aux vieux Oiseaux.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les champs, les Bois &amp; les ruisseaux","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Excitent mon plus doux ramage.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On est toûjours deconcerté,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si l’on ne chante en liberté.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Prison arrestant ma veine,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Eût ensevely mon talent :","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’Hélicon la docte Fontaine","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’est pure &amp; vive qu’en coulant.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Pour fuir, je sentois quelque envie","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’aller à la Cour de Turin ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’y croyois pouvoir sans chagrin","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Passer le reste de ma vie.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Prince m’y fit autrefois","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’honneur de me donner sa Croix ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On m’y promettoit un azile","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avec des plaisirs sans effroy :","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais un François est-il tranquile","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand il est si loin de son Roy ?","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Je n’ay jamais pû m’y resoudre.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quitter Paris m’affligeroit,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et l’ordre qui m’en banniroit,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour moy seroit un coup de foudre.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lors que je voy le Grand Loüis,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quoy que mes yeux soient ébloüis,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il me semble que je possede","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le bien qui fait tous mes desirs,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et sa presence est un remede","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui change mes maux en plaisirs.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Le seul aspect de son visage","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En sollicitant mon Procés,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"M’en promettoit un bon succés,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et fortifioit mon courage.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je disois aprés l’avoir vû,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans ces lieux regne la vertu,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On n’y souffre point d’injustice ;","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’un Roy si bon, si doux, si grand,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Conseil me sera propice,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et mon bon droit m’en est garant.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ainsi malgré la défiance,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont quelquefois j’estois surpris,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’ay demeuré ferme à Paris","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Entre la crainte &amp; l’esperance ;","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Trop heureux d’avoir attendu","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’Arrest qui vient d’estre rendu,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui finit ma peine cruelle,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui va rétablir ma santé,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui me rend mon lit, ma vaisselle,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mon repos &amp; ma liberté.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[19]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il est vray, mon bien est modique :","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais puis-je me plaindre aujourd’huy ?","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Seigneur, je suis sous vostre appuy,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’exerce un Employ pacifique.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fort peu sensible à l’interest,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Assez riche par mon Arrest,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je ne porte envie à personne,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et je me croy si bien traité,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il me semble que l’on me donne","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout ce qu’on ne m’a point ôté.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" De mes Juges toute ma vie","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je pretens chanter l’équité","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si haut, que la Posterité","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De leur vertu sera ravie.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sous un Roy juste &amp; genereux","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Leur sort sera toûjours heureux :","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On juge assez par leur conduite","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jusqu’où doit aller leur bonheur","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans une Cour, où le merite","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne peut manquer d’estre en faveur.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}}]}}}